<p>In another episode Grant revealed how his life went downhill during an addiction to painkillers.</p>

<p>The Family Feud host was on a concoction of Endone and morphine while recovering from a broken back injury after his monster truck accident.</p>

<p>The side effects from his drug use were so bad that the star once woke up surrounded by faeces and believed his wife was being raped by an intruder.</p>

